{
  "id": "RAW_edb44eb6",
  "title": "加速保护我们所有人的网络安全防御生态系统",
  "url": "https://openai.com/index/accelerating-cyber-defense-ecosystem",
  "date": "2026-04-16 00:00:00",
  "author": "OpenAI",
  "siteName": "OpenAI Blog",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div class=\"@container w-full max-w-container @md:shaded-container:px-0!\">\n   <div class=\"relative w-full\" style=\"--hero-aspect-ratio:16/9;--hero-aspect-ratio-mobile:3/4\">\n    <div class=\"multi-columns:px-0 @md:shaded-container:px-0! @container grid w-full grid-cols-12\">\n     <div class=\"col-span-12 @md:col-span-10 @md:col-start-2 @lg:col-span-8 @lg:col-start-3\">\n      <div class=\"relative flex flex-col items-center text-center\">\n       <div class=\"mb-md gap-2xs flex flex-wrap justify-center\">\n        <p class=\"text-meta text-primary-100\">\n         <br>\n        </p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"max-w-container multi-columns:px-0 multi-columns:flex @container grid w-full grid-cols-12\">\n   <div class=\"@md:col-span-6 @md:col-start-4 col-span-12 max-w-none [&amp;:not(:first-child)]:mt-sm\">\n    <p class=\"mb-sm last:mb-0\"><a class=\"transition ease-curve-a duration-250 text-primary-100 hover:text-primary-60 relative underline-offset-[0.25rem] decoration-1 underline\" href=\"https://openai.com/index/scaling-trusted-access-for-cyber-defense\"><u class=\"decoration-1 underline-offset-4\"><span>Trusted Access for Cyber</span></u>⁠</a><span> is designed around a simple premise: advanced cyber capabilities should reach defenders broadly, but access should scale with trust, validation, and safeguards. Today we’re sharing the first organizations helping put that approach into practice, from open-source security teams and vulnerability researchers to enterprises operating some of the world’s most complex digital environments.</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"@md:col-span-6 @md:col-start-4 col-span-12 max-w-none [&amp;:not(:first-child)]:mt-sm\">\n    <p class=\"mb-sm last:mb-0\"><span>The strength of this approach comes from the breadth of defenders involved. Cybersecurity is a team sport, and the systems people rely on are protected by organizations of many kinds, from major enterprises and security vendors to researchers, maintainers, public institutions, nonprofits, and smaller teams with limited security resources.</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"@md:col-span-6 @md:col-start-4 col-span-12 max-w-none [&amp;:not(:first-child)]:mt-xl\">\n    <div class=\"max-w-container @container grid w-full grid-cols-12 toc-content-heading scroll-mt-[calc(var(--header-h)+var(--toc-button-h))]\" id=\"investing-in-the-broader-ecosystem\">\n     <div class=\"full-grid-content:@md:col-span-12 full-grid-content:@md:col-start-1 col-span-12 max-w-none @md:col-span-6 @md:col-start-4\">\n      <h2 class=\"text-h3 scroll-mt-[calc(var(--header-h)+var(--toc-button-h))]\"><span>Investing in the broader ecosystem</span></h2>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"@md:col-span-6 @md:col-start-4 col-span-12 max-w-none [&amp;:not(:first-child)]:mt-sm\">\n    <p class=\"mb-sm last:mb-0\"><span>Not every organization has the benefit of a 24x7 security team who is able to respond to incidents when they are </span><a href=\"https://github.com/axios/axios/issues/10636\" class=\"transition ease-curve-a duration-250 text-primary-100 hover:text-primary-60 relative underline-offset-[0.25rem] decoration-1 underline\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><u class=\"decoration-1 underline-offset-4\"><span>disclosed on a Friday night</span></u>⁠<span class=\"sr-only\">(opens in a new window)</span></a><span>. It’s important for all software developers to benefit from the advanced cybersecurity capabilities of frontier models, which is why we’ve committed $10 million in API credits through our Cybersecurity Grant Program.&nbsp;</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"@md:col-span-6 @md:col-start-4 col-span-12 max-w-none [&amp;:not(:first-child)]:mt-sm\">\n    <p class=\"mb-sm last:mb-0\"><span>Initial recipients include </span><a href=\"https://socket.dev/\" class=\"transition ease-curve-a duration-250 text-primary-100 hover:text-primary-60 relative underline-offset-[0.25rem] decoration-1 underline\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><u class=\"decoration-1 underline-offset-4\"><span>Socket</span></u>⁠<span class=\"sr-only\">(opens in a new window)</span></a><span> and </span><a href=\"https://semgrep.dev/\" class=\"transition ease-curve-a duration-250 text-primary-100 hover:text-primary-60 relative underline-offset-[0.25rem] decoration-1 underline\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><u class=\"decoration-1 underline-offset-4\"><span>Semgrep</span></u>⁠<span class=\"sr-only\">(opens in a new window)</span></a><span>, which focus on software supply chain security, and </span><a href=\"https://calif.io\" class=\"transition ease-curve-a duration-250 text-primary-100 hover:text-primary-60 relative underline-offset-[0.25rem] decoration-1 underline\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><u class=\"decoration-1 underline-offset-4\"><span>Calif</span></u>⁠<span class=\"sr-only\">(opens in a new window)</span></a><span> and </span><a href=\"https://trailofbits.com\" class=\"transition ease-curve-a duration-250 text-primary-100 hover:text-primary-60 relative underline-offset-[0.25rem] decoration-1 underline\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><u class=\"decoration-1 underline-offset-4\"><span>Trail of Bits</span></u>⁠<span class=\"sr-only\">(opens in a new window)</span></a><span>, which pair frontier models with vulnerability research experts. We’re looking to partner with more teams that have a proven track record of identifying and remediating vulnerabilities in open source software and critical infrastructure systems—teams can apply </span><a class=\"transition ease-curve-a duration-250 text-primary-100 hover:text-primary-60 relative underline-offset-[0.25rem] decoration-1 underline\" href=\"https://openai.com/form/cybersecurity-grant-program/\"><u class=\"decoration-1 underline-offset-4\"><span>here⁠</span></u>⁠</a><span>.&nbsp;</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"@md:col-span-6 @md:col-start-4 col-span-12 max-w-none [&amp;:not(:first-child)]:mt-xl\">\n    <div class=\"max-w-container @container grid w-full grid-cols-12 toc-content-heading scroll-mt-[calc(var(--header-h)+var(--toc-button-h))]\" id=\"building-resilience-together\">\n     <div class=\"full-grid-content:@md:col-span-12 full-grid-content:@md:col-start-1 col-span-12 max-w-none @md:col-span-6 @md:col-start-4\">\n      <h2 class=\"text-h3 scroll-mt-[calc(var(--header-h)+var(--toc-button-h))]\"><span>Building resilience together</span></h2>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"@md:col-span-6 @md:col-start-4 col-span-12 max-w-none [&amp;:not(:first-child)]:mt-sm\">\n    <p class=\"mb-sm last:mb-0\"><span>The critical defenders joining this program protect digital infrastructure we all rely on, and will help us learn from real-world use, improve our safety systems, and make advanced defensive capabilities more useful across the ecosystem. These are firms that are already world-renowned for enterprise security leadership in their respective industries. The goal is to build the trust, verification, and accountability needed to make these tools available to the many defenders whose work keeps people, institutions, and critical systems safe. </span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"@md:col-span-6 @md:col-start-4 col-span-12 max-w-none [&amp;:not(:first-child)]:mt-sm\">\n    <p class=\"mb-sm last:mb-0\"><span>Companies and organizations that have already signed up to support these efforts include Bank of America, Blackrock, BNY, Citi, Cisco, CrowdStrike, Goldman Sachs, iVerify, JPMorgan Chase, Morgan Stanley, NVIDIA, Oracle, SpecterOps, and </span><a href=\"https://zscaler.com/blogs/company-news/zscaler-and-openai-join-forces-advance-next-era-cybersecurity\" class=\"transition ease-curve-a duration-250 text-primary-100 hover:text-primary-60 relative underline-offset-[0.25rem] decoration-1 underline\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><span>Zscaler</span>⁠<span class=\"sr-only\">(opens in a new window)</span></a><span>.&nbsp;</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"@md:col-span-6 @md:col-start-4 col-span-12 max-w-none [&amp;:not(:first-child)]:mt-sm\">\n    <p class=\"mb-sm last:mb-0\"><span>We have also provided access to GPT‑5.4‑Cyber to the U.S. Center for AI Standards and Innovation (CAISI) and the UK AI Security Institute (UK AISI) so that they can conduct evaluations focused on the model’s cyber capabilities and safeguards.</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"@md:col-span-6 @md:col-start-4 col-span-12 max-w-none [&amp;:not(:first-child)]:mt-sm\">\n    <p class=\"mb-sm last:mb-0\"><span>We will keep expanding Trusted Access for Cyber as we learn, with safeguards that rise with capability and pathways that help legitimate defenders move faster. We want participants to push the frontier of defensive research, share what they discover, and help turn new insights into stronger protection for everyone. Cyber defense is a shared challenge, and this program should reflect the breadth of the people and organizations doing that work every day. </span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"@md:col-span-6 @md:col-start-4 col-span-12 max-w-none [&amp;:not(:first-child)]:mt-sm\">\n    <p class=\"mb-sm last:mb-0 ps-xs @lg:ps-md\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"col-span-12 group [&amp;:not(:first-child)]:mt-sm\">\n    <section class=\"group/component-group @container\">\n     <div class=\"@container grid w-full grid-cols-12\">\n      <div class=\"col-span-12 grid w-full grid-cols-1 items-stretch gap-lg @md:gap-xl\">\n       <div class=\"gap-md flex flex-col\">\n        <nav class=\"scrollable px-sm mx-auto max-w-full scroll-mt-32 py-[4px]\" role=\"tablist\" aria-label=\"Tabs\">\n         <div class=\"relative min-w-fit\">\n          <div class=\"w-max\">\n           <div class=\"border-primary-12 p-5xs relative flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border\">\n            <button type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"true\" aria-controls=\"3PVt4NQPaVxZVwOzo2pGIR-panel\" id=\"3PVt4NQPaVxZVwOzo2pGIR\" class=\"text-cta min-h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-5xs px-2xs py-3xs rounded-full whitespace-nowrap transition-colors ease-curve-d duration-medium focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-primary-12 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 hover:bg-primary-12 bg-primary-4\"><span>BNY</span></button>\n            <button type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-controls=\"01rSwYj3BiArdTN99NFu6N-panel\" id=\"01rSwYj3BiArdTN99NFu6N\" class=\"text-cta min-h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-5xs px-2xs py-3xs rounded-full whitespace-nowrap transition-colors ease-curve-d duration-medium focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-primary-12 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 hover:bg-primary-12\"><span>CrowdStrike</span></button>\n            <button type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-controls=\"6t5ciDnGVKKJAJtlntb6wd-panel\" id=\"6t5ciDnGVKKJAJtlntb6wd\" class=\"text-cta min-h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-5xs px-2xs py-3xs rounded-full whitespace-nowrap transition-colors ease-curve-d duration-medium focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-primary-12 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 hover:bg-primary-12\"><span>Cisco</span></button>\n            <button type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-controls=\"5MUYztfe9tJRn6yhm9tD5K-panel\" id=\"5MUYztfe9tJRn6yhm9tD5K\" class=\"text-cta min-h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-5xs px-2xs py-3xs rounded-full whitespace-nowrap transition-colors ease-curve-d duration-medium focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-primary-12 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 hover:bg-primary-12\"><span>Citi</span></button>\n            <button type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-controls=\"6L70ndi1ZMrZIgL7CjvGar-panel\" id=\"6L70ndi1ZMrZIgL7CjvGar\" class=\"text-cta min-h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-5xs px-2xs py-3xs rounded-full whitespace-nowrap transition-colors ease-curve-d duration-medium focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-primary-12 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 hover:bg-primary-12\"><span>NVIDIA</span></button>\n            <button type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-controls=\"7gzTU6q7YVNeXKZRXIjep4-panel\" id=\"7gzTU6q7YVNeXKZRXIjep4\" class=\"text-cta min-h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-5xs px-2xs py-3xs rounded-full whitespace-nowrap transition-colors ease-curve-d duration-medium focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-primary-12 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 hover:bg-primary-12\"><span>Oracle</span></button>\n            <button type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-controls=\"7KkhN8kXqtVcD3FQf3fckc-panel\" id=\"7KkhN8kXqtVcD3FQf3fckc\" class=\"text-cta min-h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-5xs px-2xs py-3xs rounded-full whitespace-nowrap transition-colors ease-curve-d duration-medium focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-primary-12 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 hover:bg-primary-12\"><span>Zscaler</span></button>\n            <button type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-controls=\"1ZH3AphH5NxEmJgVznNw6p-panel\" id=\"1ZH3AphH5NxEmJgVznNw6p\" class=\"text-cta min-h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-5xs px-2xs py-3xs rounded-full whitespace-nowrap transition-colors ease-curve-d duration-medium focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-primary-12 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 hover:bg-primary-12\"><span>iVerify</span></button>\n            <button type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-controls=\"7G7xpcgnYSpHFVdQh0gJjG-panel\" id=\"7G7xpcgnYSpHFVdQh0gJjG\" class=\"text-cta min-h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-5xs px-2xs py-3xs rounded-full whitespace-nowrap transition-colors ease-curve-d duration-medium focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-primary-12 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 hover:bg-primary-12\"><span>SpecterOps</span></button>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </nav>\n        <div>\n         <div id=\"3PVt4NQPaVxZVwOzo2pGIR-panel\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"3PVt4NQPaVxZVwOzo2pGIR\" class=\"overflow-hidden transition-opacity duration-300 *:my-0!\">\n          <div class=\"max-w-container multi-columns:px-0 @container w-full\">\n           <div class=\"px-sm grid grid-cols-12 gap-y-8\">\n            <blockquote class=\"text-h3 text-primary-100 col-span-12 col-start-1 text-center font-medium tracking-tight @md:col-span-8 @md:col-start-3\">“BNY is committed to helping protect the security and resilience of the financial system as AI capabilities accelerate. We are working closely with those at the forefront of enabling these efforts. Building on our ongoing collaboration with OpenAI, we are pleased to participate in their Trusted Access for Cyber program”</blockquote>\n            <div class=\"text-primary-100 text-meta col-span-12 col-start-1 text-center text-pretty @md:col-span-6 @md:col-start-4\">—Leigh-Ann Russell, Chief Information Officer and Global Head of Engineering</div>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </section>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"@container w-full\">\n   <div class=\"@lg:max-w-container flex w-auto\">\n    <div class=\"w-full no-scrollbar snap-x snap-mandatory overflow-x-auto overflow-y-hidden\">\n     <div class=\"@md:gap-sm px-sm @md:px-md pe-sm flex min-w-224 @md:min-w-[unset] @lg:px-0 grid flex-none grid-cols-3\">\n      <div class=\"mb-md relative @md:mb-0 ps-sm snap-start @md:ps-0 min-w-[calc(100%/3)] ps-0 last:me-0\"></div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "OpenAI 宣布了其 \"可信网络访问\" 倡议下 1000 万美元网络安全资助计划的初始合作伙伴和受助者，旨在将先进的 AI 驱动网络防御能力扩展到广泛的防御者生态系统中。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "OpenAI 宣布了其 \"可信网络访问\" 倡议下 1000 万美元网络安全资助计划的初始合作伙伴和受助者，旨在将先进的 AI 驱动网络防御能力扩展到广泛的防御者生态系统中。",
  "summary": "这篇 OpenAI 博客文章详细介绍了其 \"可信网络访问\" 倡议的启动和初步进展。该计划旨在为防御者提供先进的 AI 网络安全能力，同时根据信任和安全保障来扩展访问权限。文章宣布了首批参与组织，包括 Socket 和 Semgrep 等安全供应商、Trail of Bits 等研究公司，以及美国银行、思科、CrowdStrike 和 NVIDIA 等大型企业。一个关键组成部分是价值 1000 万美元的 API 积分资助计划，旨在支持开源安全团队和漏洞研究人员。该倡议还包括向美国和英国政府 AI 安全研究所提供 GPT‑5.4‑Cyber 模型进行评估。其核心理念是网络安全是一项集体努力，需要企业、供应商、研究人员和公共机构之间的协作来构建韧性。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "OpenAI 正在通过基于信任的框架扩展对先进 AI 网络能力的访问。",
      "explanation": "\"可信网络访问\" 计划旨在让前沿模型可供广泛的防御者使用，但访问权限是经过有意控制的，并随着对接收方的验证、安全保障和已证实的可信度而逐步扩展。"
    },
    {
      "point": "一项 1000 万美元的网络安全资助计划面向更广泛的防御生态系统，特别是资源有限的团队。",
      "explanation": "为确保不仅仅是大型企业受益，OpenAI 正在向开源安全团队和漏洞研究人员提供 API 积分，首批资助对象包括 Socket、Semgrep、Calif 和 Trail of Bits。"
    },
    {
      "point": "该倡议获得了主要金融、科技和安全公司联盟的支持。",
      "explanation": "美国银行、思科、CrowdStrike、高盛、摩根大通和 NVIDIA 等行业领导者的参与，增强了该计划的可信度和实际影响力，这些公司依赖并帮助验证这些防御措施。"
    },
    {
      "point": "政府 AI 安全研究所将独立评估专门的网络模型。",
      "explanation": "OpenAI 已向美国 CAISI 和英国 AISI 提供了 GPT‑5.4‑Cyber 模型，用于对其网络能力和安全保障进行外部评估，这强调了其对安全性和问责制的承诺。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "\"可信网络访问\" 的设计基于一个简单的前提：先进的网络能力应该广泛地提供给防御者，但访问权限应随着信任、验证和安全保障而扩展。",
    "网络安全是一项团队运动，人们所依赖的系统是由多种类型的组织共同保护的。",
    "并非每个组织都拥有一个 7x24 小时待命的安全团队，能够在周五晚上事件被披露时做出响应。",
    "目标是建立必要的信任、验证和问责制，以便将这些工具提供给众多防御者，他们的工作保护着人民、机构和关键系统的安全。",
    "网络防御是一项共同的挑战，这个计划应该反映出每天从事这项工作的人员和组织的广泛性。"
  ],
